      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering peak power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains exceptionally tight, benefiting from documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution, while the suspension geometry remains factory-spec for a pure driving experience. Riding on staggered Style 67 wheels with fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, the mechanical synchronization is flawless. This is a turnkey, collector-spec vehicle for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
